# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Admin panel — never publish the CRUD interface
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
admin/
**/admin/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local persisted state. The public registry.json and site_config.json are
# shipped so the deployed site has data on first boot. Everything else
# (audit log, health cache, backups) stays local-only.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/data/backups/
**/admin_log*
**/health_cache*
**/registry.csv

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Misc
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig
